OL,3,CDrought declared in south east Wales
OL,4,Cafter driest six-months in decades
OL,6,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) has
OL,7,Fdeclared that south east Wales is now
OL,8,Fofficially in drought status.
OL,10,FIt said that the 'trigger thresholds'
OL,11,Fhave been met for the area to be moved
OL,12,Finto this category after the driest
OL,13,Fsix-months in Wales since 1976.
OL,15,FThe decision was shared in a meeting
OL,16,Fwith the Welsh Government's Drought
OL,17,FLiaison Group.
