OL,6,FRhian Thomas, Sustainable Water and
OL,7,FNature Manager from NRW said: "The
OL,8,Flack of significant rainfall has taken
OL,9,Fits toll on the environment, and we
OL,10,Fare receiving reports of low flows and
OL,11,Fdry riverbeds in some locations.
OL,13,F"South east Wales have been
OL,14,Fparticularly impacted, with rivers
OL,15,Freceiving very little rainfall in
OL,16,Frecent months, and the Usk and Wye
OL,17,Frecording persistently high river
OL,18,Ftemperatures which can threaten fish
OL,19,Fpopulations.
