OL,6,F"As the area enters into a state of
OL,7,Fdrought, we will step up actions in
OL,8,Fline with NRW's Drought Plan."
OL,10,FThe areas affected include:
OL,12,FImpacts of the drought include the
OL,13,Fdrying of private water supplies in
OL,14,Fsome areas, farmers needing to seek
OL,15,Falternative livestock watering
OL,16,Fsupplies and supplementary feeding due
OL,17,Fto reduced grass growth.
