OL,3,CDrought declared in south east Wales
OL,4,Cafter driest six-months in decades
OL,6,FPeople are advised to follow advice
OL,7,Ffrom Dwr Cymru Welsh Water and Hafren
OL,8,FDyfrdwy, and use water wisely this
OL,9,Fsummer to help ease pressures on the
OL,10,Fwater supplies - although there is no
OL,11,Fhosepipe ban in place.
OL,13,FMs Thomas added: "It is going to take
OL,14,Fconsiderable time for rivers, ground
OL,15,Fwaters and soils to recover.
OL,17,F"While many people are enjoying the
OL,18,Fsummer holidays, we're urging people
OL,19,Fto be mindful about their water use
OL,20,Fand consider how they can conserve
OL,21,Fwater at home and in work."
